name: Deep
description:
Lucy tried to remember, there was something hidden deep inside her brain, it should be something related to her past. She tried to remember how long has it been, for how long she was traveling in deep space. No clue... As she tried to remember, Daedalus sensed her neural activity and started to play a song. As Lucy's ears filled with the song, she tried to stay awake, but it was more powerful then her willpower, she fell into deep slumber.
